	<article id="post-152" class="post-152 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-art-and-culture category-film category-intelligence category-interviews category-machon category-media category-mi5 category-spies tag-annie-machon tag-dirty-tricks tag-mi5 tag-the-bank-job">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/08/publicity-for-the-film-the-bank-job-2008.html" title="Permalink to Publicity for the film, “The Bank Job” (2008)" rel="bookmark">Publicity for the film, “The Bank Job” (2008)</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/08/publicity-for-the-film-the-bank-job-2008.html" title="16:33" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2010-08-11T16:33:10+00:00" pubdate>August 11, 2010</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/08/publicity-for-the-film-the-bank-job-2008.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>I did a <span class="caps">PR</span> inter­view for the 2008 film “The Bank Job”, which was included in the extras on the <span class="caps">DVD</span>.  </p>
<p>In the inter­view I dis­cussed <span class="caps">MI5</span> dirty tricks and spy influ­ence over the media.</p>
</p>
<p class="asset asset-video" style="display: block; margin: 0pt auto;" align="center"><object type="application/x-shockwave-flash" data="http://vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf" height="400" width="500"><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true"><param name="movie" value="http://vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf"><param name="flashvars" value="clip_id=13708849&#038;color=00adef&#038;fullscreen=1&#038;server=vimeo.com&#038;show_byline=1&#038;show_portrait=1&#038;show_title=1"></object></p>
