	<article id="post-154" class="post-154 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-gaddafi category-intelligence category-law category-libya category-machon category-media category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-police category-politics category-spies category-surveillance category-talks-2 category-terrorism category-torture category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-annie-machon tag-civil-liberties-2 tag-intelligence-2 tag-mi5 tag-mi6 tag-police-2 tag-secret-garden-party tag-sgp tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2 tag-talk tag-the-forum">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/08/the-secret-garden-party-uk-2010.html" title="Permalink to The Secret Garden Party, UK 2010" rel="bookmark">The Secret Garden Party, <span class="caps">UK</span> 2010</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/08/the-secret-garden-party-uk-2010.html" title="14:50" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2010-08-11T14:50:24+00:00" pubdate>August 11, 2010</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/08/the-secret-garden-party-uk-2010.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a style="float: left;" onclick="window.open( this.href, '_blank', 'width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0' ); return false" href="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e550903031883301348622053f970c-popup.html"><img class="asset asset-image at-xid-6a00e550903031883301348622053f970c " style="margin: 0px 5px 5px 0px;" src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e550903031883301348622053f970c-320wi.jpg" alt="SGP_2010" /></a> In July I was invited back to speak at the <a href="http://www.secretgardenparty.com/2010/">Secret Garden Party</a>, a music, polit­ics, and arts fest­ival held annu­ally some­where, er, secret in the <span class="caps">UK</span>.</p>
<p>What a fab week­end.  I have a well-known anti­pathy to sleep­ing under can­vas, but this was an excel­lent fest­ival — and even the com­post loos were not too grim.  </p>
<p>Lis­ted as one of the “Star Acts” in the prin­ted fest­ival pro­gramme (I blush), I had the lux­ury of an hour and a half to speak in the première debate tent in the <a href="http://www.secretgardenparty.com/2010/#/268/296">Rebels and Intel­lec­tu­als</a> sec­tion of the fest­ival — The Forum — a concept that the organ­iser, Ben de Vere, prom­ises to trans­plant to Lon­don some­time in the near future.</p>
<p>Any­way, I ser­i­ously recom­mend put­ting this fest­ival in your diar­ies for next year, and keep an eye open for the spread of The Forum.….</p>
<p>Here’s the video:</p>
<p>
<object width="500" height="306" data="http://www.youtube.com/v/kr5KNLGlDOk?version=3" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/kr5KNLGlDOk?version=3" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /></object><br />
 </p>
</p>					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
