				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cologne" rel="tag">Cologne</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gestapo" rel="tag">Gestapo</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/machon" rel="tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nazi" rel="tag">Nazi</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/police-state" rel="tag">police state</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war" rel="tag">war</a>			</span>
						
